tests.title: Update Booking Wihtout BookingID
tests.fullTitle: Restful booker API Test Update Booking Wihtout BookingID
tests.code:
const response = await request
.put("/booking/")
.set("Accept", "application/json")
.set("Content-Type", "application/json")
.set("Cookie", "token=" + token)
.send({
    "firstname" : "Sanber",
    "lastname" : "Code",
    "totalprice" : 111555,
    "depositpaid" : true,
    "bookingdates" : {
        "checkin" : "2018-01-01",
        "checkout" : "2019-01-01"
    },
    "additionalneeds" : "Breakfast"
})
expect(response.status).to.be.eql(404);
